violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</link><description>协议中心进行的民意调查显示，犹太人和阿拉伯社区的相互不信任程度急剧上升。 “10 月 7 日的集体创伤将影响未来几年各群体之间的关系”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/90-of-jews-see-domestic-violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列和哈马斯在释放人质人数、战斗暂停持续时间方面存在分歧，谈判陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉国土报，哈马斯寻求释放约 50 名人质，其中主要是妇女和儿童，以换取释放巴勒斯坦女性和未成年囚犯。以色列要求大幅增加人质人数</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</guid></item><item><title>“甘茨离开政府的那一刻，内塔尼亚胡的沙漏就翻转了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</link><description>要求甘茨开始计划退出紧急政府的不仅仅是政治利益。甘茨的退出策略也符合国家利益</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 20:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女奋力打破全球对哈马斯性暴力的沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</link><description>与许多其他领域一样，当谈到 10 月 7 日揭露哈马斯基于性别的暴力时，以色列公民介入了政府留下的巨大空白</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 19:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</guid></item><item><title>新研究表明，大卫和所罗门的圣经王国可能确实存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-15/ty-article/david-and-solomons-biblical-kingdom-may-have-existed-after-all-new-study-suggests/0000018b-cddd-d518-a39b-fffd773b0000</link><description>圣经考古学家称，基泽的纪念性建筑可追溯到公元前 10 世纪初，这意味着它们可能是所罗门建造的。但同事们仍持怀疑态度</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 19:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-15/ty-article/david-and-solomons-biblical-kingdom-may-have-existed-after-all-new-study-suggests/0000018b-cddd-d518-a39b-fffd773b0000</guid></item><item><title>地堡破坏者、炮弹和激光制导导弹：美国向以色列提供的弹药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/shells-laser-guided-missiles-and-bunker-busters-the-munitions-the-u-s-supplied-israel/0000018b-d3b9-dffa-adef-f7b990750000</link><description>五角大楼内部文件详细介绍了“以色列高级领导人”提出的弹药要求 ■ 国会民主党人对拜登政府缺乏透明度越来越警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 17:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/shells-laser-guided-missiles-and-bunker-busters-the-munitions-the-u-s-supplied-israel/0000018b-d3b9-dffa-adef-f7b990750000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院无视政府立场，裁定犹太配偶的寡妇可以移民以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/defying-govt-position-high-court-rules-widows-of-jewish-spouse-can-immigrate-to-israel/0000018b-d21d-dffa-adef-f61d9c730000</link><description>内政部一直要求寡妇提供犹太生活方式的证明，才有资格遵守回归法，但这一条件已被高等法院最近的裁决驳回</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 17:36:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/defying-govt-position-high-court-rules-widows-of-jewish-spouse-can-immigrate-to-israel/0000018b-d21d-dffa-adef-f61d9c730000</guid></item><item><title>加沙变成废墟：世界上最大的巴勒斯坦城市很快将无法居住</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-in-ruins-the-largest-palestinian-city-in-the-world-soon-uninhabitable/0000018b-d3a4-d423-affb-f3a70ff40000</link><description>无论是在古代还是近代历史中，中东和世界各地的城市都曾经被摧毁过。对于各国来说，这是一场地震事件。正如 10 月 7 日改变了一切一样，加沙城的毁灭也将改变一切</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 16:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-in-ruins-the-largest-palestinian-city-in-the-world-soon-uninhabitable/0000018b-d3a4-d423-affb-f3a70ff40000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔调解的加沙以色列人质释放谈判取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</link><description>据路透社周三报道，卡塔尔调解员正在寻求谈判一项协议，其中包括释放约 50 名人质，以换取为期三天的停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 15:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列渴望生命，就必须改变对巴勒斯坦人的态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</guid></item><item><title>“隐蔽的反犹太主义已变得完全公开”：以色列海外学生面临仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</link><description>自以色列-加沙战争爆发以来，外国医学院的以色列学生报告称，他们发现自己受到攻击</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯屠杀了巴勒斯坦独立国家的梦想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-has-massacred-the-palestinian-dream-of-an-independent-state/0000018b-d28c-dffa-adef-f68c96400000</link><description>早在哈马斯发动袭击之前，两国解决方案就已处于生命末期，但 10 月 7 日的袭击很可能是两国解决方案棺材上的最后一颗钉子。对于以色列和巴勒斯坦的民族愿望来说，这都是一场悲剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 13:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-has-massacred-the-palestinian-dream-of-an-independent-state/0000018b-d28c-dffa-adef-f68c96400000</guid></item><item><title>伦敦画廊因反犹太主义言论推迟艾未未展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/london-gallery-postpones-exhibition-by-ai-weiwei-over-antisemitic-comments/0000018b-d2fb-dffa-adef-f6fb50670000</link><description>这位著名的中国持不同政见者在社交媒体上谈论犹太“媒体影响”和对以色列的数十亿美元援助资金，导致他原定在里森画廊举行的展览被推迟</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 13:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/london-gallery-postpones-exhibition-by-ai-weiwei-over-antisemitic-comments/0000018b-d2fb-dffa-adef-f6fb50670000</guid></item><item><title>加沙哈马斯政权的垮台不会损害伊朗的地区战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-fall-of-the-hamas-regime-in-gaza-wouldnt-harm-irans-regional-strategy/0000018b-d2b1-dffa-adef-f6b1e1860000</link><description>德黑兰与哈马斯和真主党等组织的关系并不是其安全概念的核心，因为它试图与中东各国政府建立联系</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 12:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/m